# Images Directory

This directory is for storing image assets used throughout the application.

## Structure
- `/images/` - General images (product images, news images, etc.)
- `/icons/` - Icon files
- `/logos/` - Logo files

## Usage
Images in this directory can be referenced in your code using:
- Next.js Image component: `/assets/images/your-image.jpg`
- Regular img tag: `/assets/images/your-image.jpg`
- CSS: `url('/assets/images/your-image.jpg')`

## Recommended Image Formats
- **JPG/JPEG** - For photographs and complex images
- **PNG** - For images with transparency
- **WebP** - For optimized web images (recommended)
- **SVG** - For icons and simple graphics

